Binary installer
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This archive contains binary, Bourne shell based installer. It is intended
for Unix systems running mono. To run it type:

  ./install-nemerle.sh

The installation process will additionally create uninstallation script.
The installation script doesn't take any command line parameters. It will
ask you interactively.


Known problems
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* It doesn't install nemerle.pc file.
* It doesn't install documentation.

